Kindergarten and Preschool Registration

shared_text:
Oak Hill Elementary
April 29 at 12:40 PM ·

Work Pick-Up for Oak Hill Elementary

Monday, May 4th, 2020

Work for Oak Hill Elementary Students
@ Oak Hill Elementary
10:00 AM - 12:00 PM
3:00 PM - 5:00 PM

Work pick-up will be done as a drive-thru. Cars will follow the morning student drop-off route at the front of Oak Hill Elementary. Staff will bring the packets and belongings to your car as you pull up to the door.

*** Items that may have been in a student's desk, cubby or locker will also be delivered to the parent's car.

*** Library books and classroom books can be turned in at this time. Any work may also be dropped off.

*** Spring Lifetouch pictures that were taken in February will be passed out.

*** Any work not picked up will be placed on bus routes on Thursday, May 7th during the meal distribution bus routes.***

*** Monday's lunch delivery has not been changed and will run as normal.

If you have any questions, calls can be made to the Oak Hill Elementary office.

We hope everyone is staying healthy!!! We miss you all!!!!

post_text:
Work Pick-Up for Oak Hill Elementary

Monday, April 6th, 2020

Work for Oak Hill Elementary Students
@ Oak Hill Elementary

10:00 AM - 12:00 PM
3:00 PM - 5:00 PM

Work pick-up will be done as a drive-thru. Cars will follow the morning student drop-off route at the front of Oak Hill Elementary. Staff will bring the packets to your car as you pull up to the door.

*** Any work not picked up will be placed on bus routes on Thursday, April 9th, during the meal distribution bus routes.***

*** Monday's lunch delivery has not been changed this and will run as normal. ***

*** At this time, work can be kept at home and combined with the new second work packet. Students can email pictures of work with teachers at any time. ***

If you have any questions, call can be made to the Oak Hill Elementary office on Monday, April 6th, 2020, from 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM.

We miss you all and hope everyone is staying safe and healthy!!!!
